OL,3,CStreet cordoned off following scaffold
OL,4,Ccollapse
OL,6,FA spokesperson for East Sussex Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service said: "We were
OL,8,Fcalled at 1.29pm on 18 December 2025
OL,9,Fto reports of collapsed scaffolding in
OL,10,FFirst Avenue, Hove.
OL,12,F"One fire engine from Preston Circus
OL,13,Fwas in attendance. Crews attended for
OL,14,Fscene safety, liaising with the police
OL,15,Fand the area was cordoned off.
OL,17,F"There were no reports of any injuries.
OL,19,F"Crews left the scene by 3.16pm,
OL,20,Fhanding over to the main building
OL,21,Fcontractor."
